snippet.title: Rihanna’s Pregnancy Rumors Stir Up After Spotted Holding Hands With A$AP Rocky
snippet.description:
Rihanna and A$AP Rocky are spotted holding hands on a shopping date just a few days after pregnancy rumors. Plus, Madonna claps back at 50 Cent after he mocks her bedroom photo.
#Rihanna #ASAPRocky #BillieEilish
